Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.00,0:01:41.00,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(500,500)}本字幕由豌豆字幕組&風之聖殿字幕組聯合製作 \N僅供學習交流 禁止用於商業用途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.00,0:00:35.00,zhu,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.43,0:00:10.03,oped,,0,0,0,,前所未見的瞬間 令人激動的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.36,0:00:23.54,oped,,0,0,0,,初出茅廬的我 面對充滿未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.62,0:00:35.30,oped,,0,0,0,,像那一天一色的晨空般 無數次驚訝不已
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.30,0:00:45.98,oped,,0,0,0,,現在正鐫刻歷史 胸中也滿溢思緒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.98,0:00:51.57,oped,,0,0,0,,定能創造
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:58.16,oped,,0,0,0,,前所未見的瞬間 令人激動的心靈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.16,0:01:03.79,oped,,0,0,0,,一切都光芒四射
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:09.29,oped,,0,0,0,,不為人知的自己 發現未來的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:24.56,oped,,0,0,0,,我不懈追尋 那最珍貴的寶物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:26.23,oped,,0,0,0,,永不停歇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.59,0:01:28.59,oped,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.93,0:23:01.06,oped,,0,0,0,,發生奇蹟的機率
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.44,0:23:06.57,oped,,0,0,0,,根本無法計算
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.94,0:23:12.07,oped,,0,0,0,,讓我們相遇的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:19.16,oped,,0,0,0,,或許只是神明的惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:25.30,oped,,0,0,0,,明天的天空會是什麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.09,0:23:32.09,oped,,0,0,0,,讓我們去看看 那未知的顏色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.89,0:23:39.27,oped,,0,0,0,,無法證明的心 無法證明之物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.27,0:23:44.65,oped,,0,0,0,,無法證明之事 那就是我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.90,0:23:50.40,oped,,0,0,0,,無法證明的心 無法證明之物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.40,0:23:55.99,oped,,0,0,0,,無法證明之事 那就是我的心情…或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.17,0:24:06.54,oped,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,262)}那就是我的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.67,0:24:08.67,oped,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:06.85,biaoti,,0,0,0,,小櫻的回憶觀賞會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你今天也很開心啊 秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我是不是吃相不太好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不是 只是你今天一直在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.38,0:02:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那本書 我又能讀懂新的內容了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}女孩子長出了貓的耳朵和尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.15,0:02:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}愛麗絲跟她說了之後 耳朵和尾巴就消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.64,0:02:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}之前是說到了這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.29,0:02:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.09,0:02:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}之後是 愛麗絲的朋友全都變成了各式各樣的動物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}熊 松鼠 還有綿羊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}很有趣的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}確實很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你會變成什麼動物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.59,0:02:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}兔子之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.58,0:03:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我最喜歡兔子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}書上還寫了什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}然後天氣變得很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.19,0:03:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}氣氛變得可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.67,0:03:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}之後愛麗絲努力把大家變回了原樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}希望愛麗絲能再努力一些
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.05,0:03:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}海渡？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.97,0:03:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你今天要出門吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 他們又邀請我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.05,0:03:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}祝你今天過得開開心心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.71,0:03:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}看招
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}看到沒 我的駕駛技術
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還不能看鏡子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.54,0:03:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.17,0:04:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖說今天休息 但你們一大早就這麼忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.38,0:04:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎 怎麼樣啊 我第一次弄這種髮型
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}挺好的 及格了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.66,0:04:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有這種水平的話 你就可以把頭髮留長自己編了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你一直都是這個髮型嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 每次都是爸爸給我剪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.91,0:04:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不去理髮店剪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.84,0:04:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.16,0:04:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我一直都是爸爸幫我剪的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}哥哥最近開始讓雪兔哥剪了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.74,0:04:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那你爸爸讓誰剪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}哥哥剪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}V8和直8哪個好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.41,0:04:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不不 也可以選直6 車體更輕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}說起來 小狼小時候也是阿姨幫他剪頭髮的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.43,0:05:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}說是魔法師在變強之前不能讓刀具靠近頭部 那樣很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}之後是因為他不喜歡去理髮店
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.92,0:05:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}所以一直是偉幫他剪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.47,0:05:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.09,0:05:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我是去理髮店剪的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.01,0:05:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對了 小狼在這邊是怎麼剪頭髮的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.10,0:05:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我有點擔心小狼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他發簡訊過來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}只有文字看不出是不是真的沒事了…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}打電話不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我擔心他還在睡 就沒打
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那我來打
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼 早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你還在睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}吃早飯了沒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真是的 不吃東西是不會有精神的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 是木之本她…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這話你直接跟她說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他已經起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.74,0:06:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.52,0:06:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.02,0:06:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.17,0:06:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我 我是小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}抱歉讓你擔心了 我已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我已經起床了 剛做好早飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要好好吃飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.76,0:06:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}別勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.45,0:07:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}莓鈴沒給你添麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:10.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒有 反而是她在照顧我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.04,0:07:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}其實她還挺喜歡照顧人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.03,0:07:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}她只是不太會說話 所以容易招人誤解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}她很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.22,0:07:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們今天要去大道寺家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:25.29,pm1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(880,472)}星期天 9:00 \N和秋穗匯合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你明明邀請我了 真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事 你別在意 好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.15,0:07:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝你 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.66,0:07:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你別東張西望啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.01,0:07:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事了 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.41,0:07:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他很精神吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}放心一些了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的 謝謝你 莓鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:07:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不用謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對了 我說木之本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你就是太在意那些小事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}差不多得出門了 不是有約嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.63,0:08:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻 莓鈴 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}早
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是真的沒關係嗎 我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.70,0:08:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你也是很在意這種小事的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.09,0:08:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和木之本一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.04,0:08:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}完全沒有問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.72,0:08:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是大道寺是有東西想給你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}更何況還有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.82,0:08:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}No problem, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}Thank you. That really makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你沒聽懂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.98,0:08:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這不是國中水平的英語嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.55,0:08:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們的發音太標準了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們倆都好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}讓別人教你不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.97,0:08:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}像小狼啊 詩之本啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.25,0:09:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你不介意的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真的嗎 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.04,0:09:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}總感覺這兩個人好像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.48,0:09:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請進
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不管什麼時候來 都覺得這裡好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也是 第一次來這裡的時候都不知道這是她家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}實在太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}打攪…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.94,0:09:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你還是那麼的可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.42,0:09:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}您 您好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.36,0:09:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}園美阿姨 今天您不用上班嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}今天原本一直到傍晚都有會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過我把它推遲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:09:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}所以昨天在各種打電話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.05,0:10:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻 莓鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.51,0:10:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還有初次見面的秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.53,0:10:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}初 初次見面 我叫詩之本秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.49,0:10:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}今天一定要一起喝我親手做的下午茶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.93,0:10:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗還在英國待過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好好 下午茶對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.39,0:10:26.98,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}媽媽期待了很久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.74,0:10:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請一定要嚐嚐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我去做準備了 你們好好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.59,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.89,0:10:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}下午茶 下午茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}知世的媽媽 真是個好人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}而且特別有活力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.93,0:10:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不去你房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}今天想給你們看一個東西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請進 在這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家請進 坐到前面來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.25,0:11:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我們去吧 詩之本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.61,0:11:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這裡是看電影的房間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}也可以看電影
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不過主要是用來檢查你的影片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.48,0:11:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大道寺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.36,0:11:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請喝喝看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}檸檬紅茶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.87,0:11:30.27,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:30.99,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.44,0:11:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}今天是要看什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:40.93,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}攝於友枝町 撫子祭 舞台劇「悲傷之戀」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}接下來 友枝小學6年2班的同學將為我們帶來舞台劇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這 這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗 你之前說過想看的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:11:56.43,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}知 知 知世
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:11:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也出場了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這不挺好的嗎 久違地一起看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.10,0:12:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}詩之本你坐中間吧 你是第一次看對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.51,0:12:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那我就恭敬不如從命了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻坐這裡 坐在秋穗旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家都有出演啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.07,0:12:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家的服裝都是大道寺做的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.78,0:12:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}全部都是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.62,0:12:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}果然我的演技是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對 是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對吧對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.72,0:12:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}其實這個時候 我和小狼回香港了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.02,0:12:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在暑假去學校玩的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}發現他們在排練舞台劇 然後就出演了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然之前小狼一直說不願意 就沒安排他出演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是山崎同學受傷了 就代替他上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.48,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼的演技都進步了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.09,0:13:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}之前演睡美人的時候可糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}有機會的話 那個我也想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這魔法石將成為人們爭奪的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.22,0:13:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}比起被某人奪走 還是讓它消失比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.70,0:13:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我同意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我也是這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}他用了一天就記住了台詞和舞蹈哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}一天？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}很自然 看不出是在演戲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.89,0:13:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}彷彿他心裡就這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}簡直就是公開處刑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}忍住啊 小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不 我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我的這份思念對誰都…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.57,0:14:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不 只有你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.97,0:14:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}拜託了 請忘記我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請將我從你心裡抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.38,0:14:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那時發生了地震
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.26,0:14:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這個舞台劇沒能演到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那大家沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.33,0:14:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}不行了 要害羞死了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你不用害羞的 真的很棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.73,0:14:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}其實 想給你們看的不只是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我並不擅長跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.94,0:14:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事 和會跳舞的人一起跳是最快捷的學習方法哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.37,0:14:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這魔法石將成為人們爭奪的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}比起讓它被某人奪走 還是讓它消失比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.88,0:15:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}抱歉小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}把第一個「讓它」去掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你果然拍下來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}老師也同意了 我就偶爾拍了一些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.95,0:15:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}所以可能有點瑣碎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.86,0:15:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還得練習舞蹈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.50,0:15:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我去叫老師教
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}抱歉啊 本來我來教是最好的 但我受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.15,0:15:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}老師教我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還有 以防萬一我還做了筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}謝謝你 千春
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}因為山崎同學受傷 要辛苦李同學了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.82,0:15:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這點小事沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}笑什麼笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那就拜託你教一下李同學了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}123 123
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.07,0:15:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}左右左 右左右
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:15:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}跳得很差勁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.17,0:16:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是馬上就能…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.98,0:16:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}123 123
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.77,0:16:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好 那就和公主一起跳試試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.83,0:16:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}從後面走完那裡開始哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.62,0:16:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}李同學這樣 小櫻是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}123 12…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.31,0:16:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沒事 可能是我太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.98,0:16:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我們再慢慢來一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.60,0:17:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}123 123 123 123…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.83,0:17:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.91,0:17:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小狼好厲害 我對你刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.78,0:17:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}太厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.06,0:17:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你們真的很努力地練習了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.42,0:17:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我好欣慰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}畢竟他們兩人的優點就是很認真
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.94,0:17:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}話說大道寺 你設置了幾台攝影機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.26,0:17:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻 你真的很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.18,0:17:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這個舞台劇 真想看到最後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:17:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.27,0:18:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.84,0:18:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}現在李同學也在日本
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請一定要讓我再次拍攝…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}再看一次你們演的戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.77,0:18:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}奈緒子也進入了戲劇部 就讓我們實現這個願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對了 那時知世也獨唱了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你不想看嗎 秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.90,0:18:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你也唱過歌的吧 知世 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.45,0:18:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}雖然唱過 但並不是很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.62,0:18:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我超想看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}熱情瞬間冷卻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這件衣服也是你自己做的吧 大道寺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.68,0:18:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這件也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.74,0:18:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}開始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}夕陽如火 落入草原
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}繁星璀璨 點綴夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.41,0:19:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}詩之本
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}但是 那是你們特地準備的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.92,0:19:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.88,0:19:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這不是普通的搖晃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}封印解除
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.49,0:19:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「打盹」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.19,0:20:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}快回到座位上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.58,0:20:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}木之本同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻你察覺到氣息了嗎 在房間裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.11,0:20:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好像不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.30,0:20:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小姑娘 快來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}秋穗只是我用魔法催眠了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}你要好好照顧她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.60,0:20:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}知世 我們去園美阿姨那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}請務必待在桌子下面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.14,0:20:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}注意安全
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.44,0:20:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}要走哪邊才好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}沿原路返回 那裡離廚房很近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.21,0:20:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}她真是毫不動搖啊 大道寺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.73,0:20:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}整棟宅邸都在搖晃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.27,0:20:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}知世 小櫻 你們沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.67,0:20:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我們沒事 媽媽你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:21:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}廚房的火我都關掉了 電力系統也沒有異常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.24,0:21:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}那個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.54,0:21:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}所有人都在這裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.61,0:21:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊 小櫻你沒受傷吧 其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小櫻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「打盹」
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.74,0:21:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}對不起對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}畢竟不知道會在哪裡使用魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}還在晃動 非常危險 知世你就待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.71,0:21:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}是啊 為了不讓小櫻擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.06,0:21:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小可 拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}交給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.80,0:21:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}讓你看看我的特訓成果
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.24,0:21:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}「飛翔」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.26,0:22:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}它看起來很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.24,0:22:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}似乎很親近她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}拜託了 「飛翔」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.16,0:22:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}小可
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.20,0:24:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.72,0:24:12.97,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}交給小可
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.38,0:24:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}人是善忘的生物 活在瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.66,0:24:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}又到了「交給小可」的環節
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.16,0:24:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}這次介紹的是詩之本秋穂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.20,0:24:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}卷卷的頭髮超級可愛 唱歌也很好聽
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.91,0:24:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}在英國義大利德國法國香港日本居住過
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.26,0:24:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}只學了日語的敬語 不管和誰說話都很有禮貌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.64,0:24:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}能說很多國家的語言
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.20,0:24:34.20,zhu,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}會多種語言
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.00,0:24:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}會… 會啥 小提琴？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.72,0:24:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}說關西腔我可不會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.31,0:24:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我還真是潛力股啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.34,0:24:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}聽到沒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.60,0:24:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}我和苺鈴一起離開知世家 在回家路上
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.46,0:24:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}遇到了一個穿著中國風服裝的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.18,0:24:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}難道她也是卡牌嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.00,0:24:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}下集 小櫻和苺鈴的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.95,0:24:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}和小櫻一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.35,0:24:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}封印解除
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.62,0:24:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5}
